The effect of felzartamab treatment on classifier and PBT scores was assessed by an aligned-rank transformed analysis of variance (ART-ANOVA)34,35. The effect of treatment was assessed as the interaction term between treatment group and follow-up visit. The random effect of patient was included in the model to handle repeated measurements (equation (1))1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
